@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rlhmir(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(0.83)
    v1 = ((0.08 + wp.sin(v1 + 0.74)) * v1)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.26) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.84 / v1 + 0.83)))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v0 + 0.04) + (v0 + 0.55 / v2 + 0.05)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(tmp) / ((tmp + 0.65 - v0 + 0.94) / 0.91))
    v1 = wp.sin(v1)
    v0 = 0.85
    data[tid] = v0
